	<h1 class="title">为何美甲店越来越多，指甲油的销量却越来越差？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/11/small/11.jpg?1399473966" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">吴亭蓉</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-08-26 15:26:43 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/2030/medium/2030.jpg?1436647459" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="2030" data-title="《为何美甲店越来越多，指甲油的销量却越来越差？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/2030/medium/2030.jpg?1436647459" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/2030.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
